commentBody:
If you think about all the inquiries, depositions and meetings surrounding this impeachment,  climate change comes to mind.  Yes, this impeachment is leaving a carbon foot print on our environment and there is scientific evidence to support it.  
Please save our planet with a censure instead of impeachment then  re-elect Trump and move on.
